# Secrets — never commit these
# kubernetes/secrets/ contains K8s Secret YAML templates with REPLACE_ME
# placeholders. Fill in real values locally and apply with kubectl.
# Templates: rabbitmq-credentials, rabbitmq-app-credentials,
#            voice-pipeline-secrets, alertmanager-slack-secret
.env
*.pem
*.key
credentials.json
kubernetes/secrets/

